Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.12,0:00:22.20,OP中文,,0,0,0,,我们在零重力之中起舞
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.42,0:00:27.50,OP中文,,0,0,0,,飞速旅行到遥远的星际
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.44,0:00:35.44,OP中文,,0,0,0,,需要特殊的快递吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.92,0:00:38.00,OP中文,,0,0,0,,只需叫上Malo Korrigan
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.08,0:00:41.24,OP中文,,0,0,0,,但不是免费的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.62,0:00:48.37,OP中文,,0,0,0,,Malo Korrigan
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.92,0:00:52.02,OP中文,,0,0,0,,没人能打倒你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.20,0:00:54.70,OP中文,,0,0,0,,Malo Korrigan
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.40,0:00:57.88,OP中文,,0,0,0,,生活在宇宙中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.12,0:00:22.20,OP英文,,0,0,0,,We can dance in zero G
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.42,0:00:27.50,OP英文,,0,0,0,,Traveling fast far from galaxy
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.44,0:00:35.44,OP英文,,0,0,0,,Need a special delivery
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.92,0:00:38.00,OP英文,,0,0,0,,Just call Malo Korrigan
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.08,0:00:41.24,OP英文,,0,0,0,,But it's not free
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.62,0:00:48.37,OP英文,,0,0,0,,Malo Korrigan
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.92,0:00:52.02,OP英文,,0,0,0,,Nobody will bring you down
