Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.42,0:01:08.70,MK标题,,0,0,0,,{\pos(451.5,303)}{\fad(1820,900)}{\blur4}#4        大鼠
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.95,0:01:19.27,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Roberta, we are in the middle of some strange ionic phenomena.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.17,0:01:27.32,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Never seen anything like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.35,0:01:28.42,MK英文,,0,0,0,,It's glowing all around me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.25,0:01:31.10,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Oh, where exactly are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.20,0:01:32.70,MK英文,,0,0,0,,I'm heading towards {\u1}CO Lovas{\u0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.80,0:01:35.72,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Hmm, it's on the NKX5
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.72,0:01:38.70,MK英文,,0,0,0,,and must be the soul of a brief alizarin supernova.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.77,0:01:44.10,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Well, anyway, it looks pretty festive around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.87,0:01:55.82,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Look they're so something's just like there's 20 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.27,0:01:58.65,MK英文,,0,0,0,,You're glowing because of the static electricity
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.05,0:02:00.95,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.57,0:02:05.62,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Don't touch anything or anyone until you're out of the area.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.15,0:02:11.27,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Oh I guess Roberta was right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.82,0:02:23.50,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Kiwk, Kiwk?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.20,0:02:28.00,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Kiwk Kiwk, where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.20,0:02:29.62,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Jonas, I need a damage report.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.62,0:02:30.50,MK英文,,0,0,0,,What's our situation?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.35,0:02:33.77,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Jonas?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.82,0:02:47.80,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Jonas?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.37,0:02:50.15,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.00,0:02:55.80,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Jonas?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.80,0:03:02.90,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Oh, Jonas, where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.57,0:03:06.42,MK英文,,0,0,0,,{\u1}Holy ark!{\u0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.87,0:03:08.10,MK英文,,0,0,0,,I'm right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.90,0:03:11.32,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Checking out the damage.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.82,0:03:13.12,MK英文,,0,0,0,,So?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.50,0:03:15.55,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Nothing serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.67,0:03:17.27,MK英文,,0,0,0,,But the main problem is that
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.32,0:03:20.82,MK英文,,0,0,0,,the ship is charged with 20 million volts of static electricity
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.30,0:03:24.05,MK英文,,0,0,0,,and they're gonna discharge as soon as we touch the ground
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.17,0:03:25.27,MK英文,,0,0,0,,and then kaboom.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.57,0:03:26.27,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Is that all?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.02,0:03:30.92,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Everything within a kilometer, the Starduke, we'll burn to a crisp.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.65,0:03:44.50,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Okay, we will land on the nearest uninhabited asteroid.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.80,0:03:47.02,MK英文,,0,0,0,,In the meantime, Cyana,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.02,0:03:49.22,MK英文,,0,0,0,,could you bring our passengers a little something to eat
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.22,0:03:50.60,MK英文,,0,0,0,,and make sure they're comfortable?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.75,0:03:54.02,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Oh, whatever you say.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.25,0:04:02.40,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.42,0:04:10.32,MK英文,,0,0,0,,I can't believe that some people call this lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.22,0:04:47.62,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Come and get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.90,0:05:18.02,MK英文,,0,0,0,,The nearest asteroid,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.37,0:05:20.10,MK英文,,0,0,0,,that the SDX7,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.52,0:05:22.45,MK英文,,0,0,0,,the coordinates are 28-32,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.65,0:05:24.40,MK英文,,0,0,0,,I'll find out more and then I'll get back to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.62,0:05:25.35,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.47,0:05:26.65,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Thanks Roberta.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.47,0:05:30.77,MK英文,,0,0,0,,So, are our passengers good?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.47,0:05:35.70,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Why in the world would you have accepted to take those x2 creatures?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.57,0:05:37.90,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Because they're paying for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.30,0:05:44.60,MK英文,,0,0,0,,You know, princess, the Daisukis are quite famous on {\u1}CO Lovas{\u0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.95,0:05:45.95,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Famous for what?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.00,0:05:47.30,MK英文,,0,0,0,,For scaring little children?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.70,0:05:51.95,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Listen, Cyana, all extraterrestrials have their own characteristics.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.47,0:06:05.60,MK英文,,0,0,0,,There it is, SDX7.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.62,0:06:06.80,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Strange-looking rock.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.15,0:06:08.62,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Looks like overcooked gummy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.59,0:06:10.72,MK英文,,0,0,0,,All right now. Hang on site.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.82,0:06:11.82,MK英文,,0,0,0,,This is gonna be rough.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.42,0:06:42.90,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Holy comics!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.05,0:06:43.90,MK英文,,0,0,0,,We're gonna flip over.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.05,0:07:07.07,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Wasn't so bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.87,0:07:09.52,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Piece of cake, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.47,0:07:21.22,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Jonas, how's my baby doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.60,0:07:23.47,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Jonas.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.25,0:07:27.30,MK英文,,0,0,0,,All right I'm coming. I'm coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.30,0:07:31.22,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Well, electricity discharged.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.72,0:07:33.52,MK英文,,0,0,0,,You'll buy repairs to the cockpit
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.57,0:07:35.65,MK英文,,0,0,0,,and we'll have enough energy to get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.32,0:07:38.75,MK英文,,0,0,0,,But it'll still be a good idea to check outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.37,0:07:40.35,MK英文,,0,0,0,,I'll take care of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.82,0:08:02.00,MK英文,,0,0,0,,What a strange place.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.87,0:08:29.12,MK英文,,0,0,0,,How'd you look out there?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.40,0:08:32.62,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Not great but we should be able to take off.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.20,0:08:33.75,MK英文,,0,0,0,,I'm coming in.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.17,0:08:57.42,MK英文,,0,0,0,,I'm... I'm almost done.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.50,0:09:01.67,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Kiwk Kiwk?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.45,0:09:19.65,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Leave Kiwk Kiwk alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.07,0:09:29.67,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Kiwk Kiwk, are you alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.17,0:09:33.67,MK英文,,0,0,0,,You better stay with Jonas.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.55,0:09:48.12,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Get back to your room now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.12,0:09:49.27,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Recess is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.25,0:09:56.45,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Get away from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.25,0:10:14.05,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Everything alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.07,0:10:18.30,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Oh, our passengers were exploring.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.95,0:10:20.05,MK英文,,0,0,0,,I got them back in though.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.87,0:10:22.82,MK英文,,0,0,0,,They really give me the creeps.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.25,0:10:24.92,MK英文,,0,0,0,,I wonder what they must think of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.92,0:10:26.92,MK英文,,0,0,0,,I'd rather not talk about it if you don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.57,0:10:28.45,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Can we go?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.92,0:10:31.10,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Right away, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.57,0:10:43.72,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Shut it down.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.30,0:11:13.35,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Strange. There wasn't anything here a minute ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.75,0:11:16.35,MK英文,,0,0,0,,It's like these rocks climbed up the side of a Starduke.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.95,0:11:27.05,MK英文,,0,0,0,,It looks like it stuck in a black ice.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.45,0:11:29.00,MK英文,,0,0,0,,You used to have a boat on earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.80,0:11:30.95,MK英文,,0,0,0,,How would they get out of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.20,0:11:32.67,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Some would wait for it to melt.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.37,0:11:36.02,MK英文,,0,0,0,,But I prefer to help the process along a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.90,0:11:42.42,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Malo, this is important.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.17,0:11:46.42,MK英文,,0,0,0,,I just find out the SDX7 is a Class S asteroid.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.77,0:11:48.67,MK英文,,0,0,0,,You need a special authorization to land.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.15,0:11:51.75,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Do not go near it under any circumstances.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.07,0:11:53.65,MK英文,,0,0,0,,The consequences could be fatal.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.72,0:12:01.70,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Kiwk Kiwk?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.85,0:12:06.47,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.92,0:12:12.15,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Hold on tight.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.62,0:12:24.97,MK英文,,0,0,0,,You better hang out to your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.52,0:12:55.52,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Well, that was a waste to explosives.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.12,0:13:37.50,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Great globular clusters.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.20,0:13:42.77,MK英文,,0,0,0,,I'm not gonna let those slugs eat away the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.50,0:13:50.42,MK英文,,0,0,0,,I see that old thing is still as good as ever?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.45,0:13:55.42,MK英文,,0,0,0,,I'm telling you I just fixed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.15,0:14:09.50,MK英文,,0,0,0,,If the entire asteroid was...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.50,0:14:10.57,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Holy comics.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.00,0:14:13.12,MK英文,,0,0,0,,I don't think that slug is very happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.92,0:15:48.55,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Cyana!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.02,0:15:52.72,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Our friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.65,0:15:57.42,MK英文,,0,0,0,,But I understand you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.80,0:16:03.52,MK英文,,0,0,0,,We have entered your mind and now we are able to communicate.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.67,0:16:09.45,MK英文,,0,0,0,,And we have also entered the mind of the asteroid.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.72,0:16:12.25,MK英文,,0,0,0,,It is alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.55,0:16:15.75,MK英文,,0,0,0,,That is why it is defending himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.80,0:16:17.67,MK英文,,0,0,0,,It's alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.72,0:16:20.82,MK英文,,0,0,0,,It suffers from our friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.00,0:16:26.22,MK英文,,0,0,0,,And from any even greater evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.80,0:16:28.07,MK英文,,0,0,0,,But what can we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.82,0:16:31.20,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Cure it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.02,0:16:34.90,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Cure it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.20,0:16:54.20,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Well, looks like we have no choice
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.25,0:16:55.30,MK英文,,0,0,0,,but to shoot our way out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.80,0:16:58.05,MK英文,,0,0,0,,I'll show them what kind of proton's a meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.40,0:17:01.10,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Malo, Jonas, where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.62,0:17:02.82,MK英文,,0,0,0,,We're in a pile of trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.60,0:17:04.77,MK英文,,0,0,0,,What's the situation on the ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.30,0:17:06.75,MK英文,,0,0,0,,What can you see from where you are?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.25,0:17:09.70,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Nothing but a giant maggots.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.37,0:17:17.22,MK英文,,0,0,0,,There's some sort of metal structure.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.22,0:17:18.15,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Looks like a probe.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.50,0:17:19.40,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Yes that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.40,0:17:21.10,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Do you have any Z-17 left?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.35,0:17:22.37,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.63,0:17:24.77,MK英文,,0,0,0,,And I'm gonna feed into the slugs for dinner
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.78,0:17:27.20,MK英文,,0,0,0,,if they keep this up with a cop going to the chef.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.92,0:17:28.66,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.70,0:17:29.52,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Hang on to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.52,0:17:30.58,MK英文,,0,0,0,,But we're gonna need it later.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.84,0:17:32.78,MK英文,,0,0,0,,First step. Get closer to the probe.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.52,0:17:35.02,MK英文,,0,0,0,,She lost her mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.34,0:17:39.04,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Oh, I figured out what's happening here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.60,0:17:41.01,MK英文,,0,0,0,,This is just an asteroid.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.73,0:17:42.90,MK英文,,0,0,0,,This rock's alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.92,0:17:44.85,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Yeah, alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.44,0:17:47.72,MK英文,,0,0,0,,So you lost your mind too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.16,0:17:50.12,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Ok, old tracer, just say when.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.98,0:17:56.21,MK英文,,0,0,0,,They're fools and surrounding my fools.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.69,0:18:22.13,MK英文,,0,0,0,,It's a mining bro left by the Consortium.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.12,0:18:25.17,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Cyana, we are in the position.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.22,0:18:26.92,MK英文,,0,0,0,,How did you know there was a program?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.35,0:18:28.90,MK英文,,0,0,0,,The asteroid told the rats.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.90,0:18:30.40,MK英文,,0,0,0,,And they told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.40,0:18:32.12,MK英文,,0,0,0,,You won that bet again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.22,0:18:33.97,MK英文,,0,0,0,,What can we say, Jonas.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.97,0:18:36.12,MK英文,,0,0,0,,The asteroid is a lonely king.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.62,0:18:38.32,MK英文,,0,0,0,,The probe is making him suffer.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.82,0:18:39.62,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.67,0:18:42.20,MK英文,,0,0,0,,And those Gigantic robot is just a failure.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.27,0:18:44.17,MK英文,,0,0,0,,And then, we gonna keep them ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.32,0:18:50.67,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Jonas, you set these explosives.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.67,0:18:52.20,MK英文,,0,0,0,,I take care of those slugs.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.30,0:18:56.20,MK英文,,0,0,0,,To attract inner guards, you have to become a virus.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.72,0:19:32.60,MK英文,,0,0,0,,He's totally out of his mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.50,0:19:56.80,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Hey, fellas! It's nothing to see over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.77,0:20:53.32,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.87,0:21:16.05,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Holy supernovas! What an explosion!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.85,0:21:18.82,MK英文,,0,0,0,,The asteroid is cured.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.15,0:21:20.75,MK英文,,0,0,0,,And Malo?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.75,0:21:21.92,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Well there...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.70,0:21:25.25,MK英文,,0,0,0,,There were slugs all around the probe and...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.87,0:21:26.97,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Malo he...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.42,0:21:43.20,MK英文,,0,0,0,,And Malo he... What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.40,0:21:47.20,MK英文,,0,0,0,,He just went for a walk and stretch his legs out a little bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.82,0:21:49.87,MK英文,,0,0,0,,So, what's happened to the slugs?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.00,0:21:51.70,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Well I told them I was a friend of yours
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.72,0:21:52.80,MK英文,,0,0,0,,and then scared them off.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.25,0:21:54.30,MK英文,,0,0,0,,What's the deal with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.37,0:21:55.97,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Everything's been taken care of.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.22,0:21:58.85,MK英文,,0,0,0,,I think we can leave the asteroid now, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.22,0:22:09.92,MK英文,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.35,0:22:12.40,MK英文,,0,0,0,,So I'm not let to say hello to my friend now?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.42,0:22:13.60,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Of course you're.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.65,0:22:14.57,MK英文,,0,0,0,,That's normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.77,0:22:17.20,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Because she's loved shaking with their little tentacles.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.00,0:22:32.35,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Malo, Cyana, finally you're back.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.72,0:22:33.60,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Did you get my message?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.72,0:22:38.72,MK英文,,0,0,0,,SDX7 is a Class S asteroid, you mustn't land on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.80,0:22:41.87,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Roberta. But you're a little late.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.40,0:22:42.95,MK英文,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.40,0:22:44.90,MK英文,,0,0,0,,You landed on it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.57,0:22:46.92,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Well, how was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.50,0:22:49.80,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Uh, routine.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.40,0:23:11.30,OP中文,,0,0,0,,我们在零重力之中起舞
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.53,0:23:15.00,OP中文,,0,0,0,,飞速旅行到遥远的星际
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.18,0:23:17.55,OP中文,,0,0,0,,Malo Korrigan
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.35,0:23:21.38,OP中文,,0,0,0,,没人能打倒你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.58,0:23:24.06,OP中文,,0,0,0,,Malo Korrigan
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.90,0:23:26.95,OP中文,,0,0,0,,生活在宇宙中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.40,0:23:11.30,OP英文,,0,0,0,,We can dance in zero G{\pos(480,45)}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.53,0:23:15.00,OP英文,,0,0,0,,Traveling fast far from galaxy{\pos(480,45)}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.18,0:23:17.55,OP英文,,0,0,0,,Malo Korrigan{\pos(480,45)}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.35,0:23:21.38,OP英文,,0,0,0,,Nobody will bring you down{\pos(480,45)}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.58,0:23:24.06,OP英文,,0,0,0,,Malo Korrigan{\pos(480,45)}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.90,0:23:26.95,OP英文,,0,0,0,,live in space{\pos(480,45)}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.95,0:01:19.27,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,Roberta 我们在某种奇怪的离子物质中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.17,0:01:27.32,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,从没见过这种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.35,0:01:28.42,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,它就在我周围发光
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.25,0:01:31.10,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,哦 那你具体在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.20,0:01:32.70,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,我正前往{\u1}CO Lovas{\u0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.80,0:01:35.72,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,恩 它在NKX5
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.72,0:01:38.70,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,它是一个寿命短暂的超红巨星的残骸
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.77,0:01:44.10,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,好吧 不管怎样 这儿看起来挺有节日气氛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.87,0:01:55.82,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,它们就像20年前那样
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.27,0:01:58.65,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,由于静电的作用导致你们在发光.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.05,0:02:00.95,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,哦 这没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.57,0:02:05.62,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,在离开这片区域前不要触摸任何东西或者任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.15,0:02:11.27,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,哦 我猜Roberta是对的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.82,0:02:23.50,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,Kiwk Kiwk
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.20,0:02:28.00,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,Kiwk Kiwk 你在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.20,0:02:29.62,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,Jonas 我需要损失报告
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.62,0:02:30.50,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,我们现在怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.35,0:02:33.77,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,Jonas
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.82,0:02:47.80,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,Jonas
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.37,0:02:50.15,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,有人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.00,0:02:55.80,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,Jonas
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.80,0:03:02.90,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,哦 Jonas 你在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.57,0:03:06.42,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,天哪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.87,0:03:08.10,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,我就在这儿
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.90,0:03:11.32,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,检查故障
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.82,0:03:13.12,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,有什么问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.50,0:03:15.55,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,没什么大不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.67,0:03:17.27,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,但主要问题是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.32,0:03:20.82,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,飞船被充上了2千万伏的静电荷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.30,0:03:24.05,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,而我们接触地面时就会放电
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.17,0:03:25.27,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,接着爆炸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.57,0:03:26.27,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,这有问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.02,0:03:30.92,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,一公里之内的所有东西包括星爵号都会被炸成碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.65,0:03:44.50,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,好吧 我们就近降落在无人小行星上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.80,0:03:47.02,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,与此同时 Cyana
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.02,0:03:49.22,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,你能给我们的乘客吃点什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.22,0:03:50.60,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,并确保他们处在舒适的环境中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.75,0:03:54.02,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,哦 随你怎么说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.25,0:04:02.40,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,呃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.42,0:04:10.32,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,我真不敢相信有些人把这个当饭吃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.22,0:04:47.62,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,过来吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.90,0:05:18.02,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,最近的小行星
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.37,0:05:20.10,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,叫SDX7
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.52,0:05:22.45,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,坐标是28-32
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.65,0:05:24.40,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,等我查阅更多信息之后再跟你联系
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.62,0:05:25.35,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.47,0:05:26.65,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,谢谢你 Roberta
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.47,0:05:30.77,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,我们的乘客还好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.47,0:05:35.70,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,你为啥能接受这些乘客
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.57,0:05:37.90,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,因为他们付了钱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.30,0:05:44.60,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,你知道的 公主 大鼠种族在{\u1}CO Lovas{\u0}可是相当受欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.95,0:05:45.95,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,因什么而受欢迎啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.00,0:05:47.30,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,吓唬小朋友吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.70,0:05:51.95,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,Cyana 所有外星种族都有着他们独特的特征
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.47,0:06:05.60,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,这就是SDX7
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.62,0:06:06.80,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,是个很奇怪的石头
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.15,0:06:08.62,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,看起来像烤糊了的胶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.59,0:06:10.72,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,现在好了 大家扶稳了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.82,0:06:11.82,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,这会有点颠簸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.42,0:06:42.90,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,天哪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.05,0:06:43.90,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,我们要翻滚一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.05,0:07:07.07,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,还好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.87,0:07:09.52,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,实际上还挺简单
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.47,0:07:21.22,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,Jonas 飞船怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.60,0:07:23.47,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,Jonas
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.25,0:07:27.30,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,好了 我来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.30,0:07:31.22,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,好的 电荷都释放掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.72,0:07:33.52,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,你得为驾驶舱买备件了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.57,0:07:35.65,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,接着我们就有足够的动力离开这里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.32,0:07:38.75,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,当然 最好还是出去检查一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.37,0:07:40.35,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,我来去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.82,0:08:02.00,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,这地方真奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.87,0:08:29.12,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,你在外面检查得怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.40,0:08:32.62,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,不是很好 但我们应该可以起飞
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.20,0:08:33.75,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,我进来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.17,0:08:57.42,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,我很快就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.50,0:09:01.67,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,Kiwk Kiwk
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.45,0:09:19.65,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,放开Kiwk Kiwk
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.07,0:09:29.67,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,Kiwk Kiwk 你还好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.17,0:09:33.67,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,你最好和Jonas呆一块
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.55,0:09:48.12,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,现在赶快回到你们的舱室去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.12,0:09:49.27,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,休息已经结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.25,0:09:56.45,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.25,0:10:14.05,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,一切都还好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.07,0:10:18.30,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,哦 我们的乘客之前在四处闲逛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.95,0:10:20.05,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,不过我让他们都回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.87,0:10:22.82,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,他们真的让我脊背发冷
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.25,0:10:24.92,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,我正好奇他们该怎么看待我们的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.92,0:10:26.92,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,如果你不介意 我并不想提起此事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.57,0:10:28.45,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,我们能出发了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.92,0:10:31.10,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,没问题 女士
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.57,0:10:43.72,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,关掉它
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.30,0:11:13.35,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,奇怪 一分钟前这儿并没有东西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.75,0:11:16.35,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,看起来这些岩石爬到了星爵号的一边
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.95,0:11:27.05,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,看起来像是卡在了黑色的冰块中
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.45,0:11:29.00,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,在地球的时候你曾开着水里的船
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.80,0:11:30.95,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,就会想着怎么把这些东西搞下来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.20,0:11:32.67,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,有些人会一直等着它们融化
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.37,0:11:36.02,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,但是我希望这个过程能快一点
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.90,0:11:42.42,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,Malo 这很重要
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.17,0:11:46.42,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,我刚刚发现SDX7是一个等级S的小行星
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.77,0:11:48.67,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,你着陆的时候需要特别的许可
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.15,0:11:51.75,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,在任何情况下都不要靠近它
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.07,0:11:53.65,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,后果可能致命
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.72,0:12:01.70,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,Kiwk Kiwk
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.85,0:12:06.47,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,过来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.92,0:12:12.15,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,抓稳了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.62,0:12:24.97,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,你最好抓住你的头
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.52,0:12:55.52,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,看起来浪费了炸药
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.12,0:13:37.50,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,天哪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.20,0:13:42.77,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,我不会让那些蛞蝓吃掉我的飞船
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.50,0:13:50.42,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,这老东西依然和之前一样好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.45,0:13:55.42,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,我跟你说我刚修复了它
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.15,0:14:09.50,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,如果这整个小行星都是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.50,0:14:10.57,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,天哪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.00,0:14:13.12,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,我不认为这个蛞蝓心情很好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.92,0:15:48.55,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,Cyana
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.02,0:15:52.72,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,我们的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.65,0:15:57.42,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,我怎么听懂了你说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.80,0:16:03.52,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,我们进到了你的脑海中 这样就能沟通了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.67,0:16:09.45,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,而且我们也进入到了小行星的脑海中
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.72,0:16:12.25,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,它是活着的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.55,0:16:15.75,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,这就是为什么他在保卫自己
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.80,0:16:17.67,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,它活着吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.72,0:16:20.82,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,我们的朋友正在损害它
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.00,0:16:26.22,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,甚至一些更强大的恶魔也在摧残它
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.80,0:16:28.07,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,那我们能做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.82,0:16:31.20,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,治好它
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.02,0:16:34.90,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,治好它
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.20,0:16:54.20,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,好吧 看起来我们只能
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.25,0:16:55.30,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,杀出一条血路
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.80,0:16:58.05,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,我会告诉他们质子枪如何烧制出一顿饭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.40,0:17:01.10,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,Malo Jonas 你们在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.62,0:17:02.82,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,我们身处一堆麻烦当中
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.60,0:17:04.77,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,船上的情况如何
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.30,0:17:06.75,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,你们那儿能看到什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.25,0:17:09.70,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,除了大虫子以外没看到啥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.37,0:17:17.22,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,那边好像有个金属建筑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.22,0:17:18.15,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,看起来像是个探测器
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.50,0:17:19.40,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,就是那玩意儿
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.40,0:17:21.10,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,你们还有Z-17炸药吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.35,0:17:22.37,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.63,0:17:24.77,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,我正准备当作晚餐喂给那些蛞蝓
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.78,0:17:27.20,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,如果他们还继续作乱 那警察也得把他们拿来做饭
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.92,0:17:28.66,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.70,0:17:29.52,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,坚持住
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.52,0:17:30.58,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,我们过会才需要它
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.84,0:17:32.78,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,第一步 靠近探测器
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.52,0:17:35.02,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,她疯了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.34,0:17:39.04,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,哦 我大概知道这儿发生了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.60,0:17:41.01,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,这只是个小行星
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.73,0:17:42.90,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,这块石头是活着的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.92,0:17:44.85,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,好吧没错
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.44,0:17:47.72,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,你也疯了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.16,0:17:50.12,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,老伙计 就等你了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.98,0:17:56.21,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,这些蠢家伙围着我的蠢同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.69,0:18:22.13,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,这是个财团留下的挖矿机器人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.12,0:18:25.17,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,Cyana 我们就位了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.22,0:18:26.92,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,你怎么知道这件事的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.35,0:18:28.90,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,小行星把这件事跟大鼠说了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.90,0:18:30.40,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,然后大鼠又转告给我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.40,0:18:32.12,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,你又赌赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.22,0:18:33.97,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,这事儿挺绝的 Jonas
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.97,0:18:36.12,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,这个小行星是个孤独的国王
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.62,0:18:38.32,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,探测器正在摧残着小行星
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.82,0:18:39.62,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.67,0:18:42.20,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,而这个巨大的机器人不过是个失败品
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.27,0:18:44.17,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,不过我们会解决这个问题
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.32,0:18:50.67,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,Jonas 你来放置炸弹
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.67,0:18:52.20,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,我来处置这些蛞蝓
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.30,0:18:56.20,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,为了吸引这些免疫细胞 你需要变成病毒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.72,0:19:32.60,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,他完全疯掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.50,0:19:56.80,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,嘿 伙计们 那儿没啥好注意的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.77,0:20:53.32,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.87,0:21:16.05,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,真是巨大的爆炸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.85,0:21:18.82,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,小行星被治愈了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.15,0:21:20.75,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,而Malo呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.75,0:21:21.92,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.70,0:21:25.25,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,探测器周围有些蛞蝓
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.87,0:21:26.97,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,Malo他
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.42,0:21:43.20,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,咋了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.40,0:21:47.20,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,他只是出去散了回步
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.82,0:21:49.87,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,那这些蛞蝓呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.00,0:21:51.70,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,我说了我是你们的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.72,0:21:52.80,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,就把它们吓跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.25,0:21:54.30,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,你这边怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.37,0:21:55.97,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,所有东西都处理得很好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.22,0:21:58.85,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,船长 我觉得我们可以离开小行星了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.22,0:22:09.92,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.35,0:22:12.40,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,难道我不能和我的朋友打招呼了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.42,0:22:13.60,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,你当然可以
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.65,0:22:14.57,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,这很正常
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.77,0:22:17.20,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,因为她很喜欢和大鼠的小手握在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.00,0:22:32.35,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,Malo Cyana 你们终于回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.72,0:22:33.60,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,你们收到了我的消息吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.72,0:22:38.72,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,SDX7是一个S等级的小行星 你不可以降落在上面
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.80,0:22:41.87,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,谢谢你 Roberta 不过你说的有点晚
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.40,0:22:42.95,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.40,0:22:44.90,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,你在上面降落了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.57,0:22:46.92,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,那地方究竟如何
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.50,0:22:49.80,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,呃 例行公事而已
